stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Plan Created
    
    Draft --> Active: Admin Activates
    Active --> Inactive: Admin Deactivates
    Inactive --> Active: Admin Reactivates
    
    Active --> Subscribed: User Purchases
    Subscribed --> Trial: Start Free Trial
    Trial --> Subscribed: Trial Ends
    
    Subscribed --> Cancelled: User Cancels
    Subscribed --> Expired: Payment Failed
    Subscribed --> Active: Subscription Ends
    
    Cancelled --> [*]: End of Life
    Expired --> [*]: End of Life
    Inactive --> [*]: Plan Deleted
    
    note right of Draft
        Draft: Plan created but not visible
    end note
    
    note right of Active
        Active: Available for purchase
    end note
    
    note right of Subscribed
        Subscribed: User has active subscription
    end note
    
    note right of Trial
        Trial: Free trial period (14 days)
    end note
    
    note right of Cancelled
        Cancelled: User cancelled, valid until period end
    end note
    
    note right of Expired
        Expired: Payment failed, access revoked
    end note
